{"tid":1093603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"閪人：黃毓民 仇思達 (反獨奶共)  ;  傻閪：杜汶凙 盤菜瑩子 仇益友 (無腦信徒)","createTime":"2019-04-05T17:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T05:06:48.000Z","uid":219007,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed3332f402569effa958035ad7f96bc4c1af33c","tid":1093603,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩大類：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第一類 - 閪人類：黃毓民 / 仇思達<br />\n<br />\n奶國民黨共產黨韓國瑜，反台獨反港獨<br />\n對本土派用完即棄<br />\n<br />\n證據：<br />\n<br />\n仇思達：民族論正垃圾！拎去吻屎都嫌你臭！ 黃毓民：你班濕鳩本土派港獨有乜撚野閪用？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1093436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1093436</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[突發] 毓民屌柒本土派/港獨派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1093075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1093075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n第二類 - 傻閪類：杜汶凙 盤菜瑩子 仇益友 <br />\n<br />\nOn9黃教信徒，黃毓民跟尾狗<br />\n反泛民反上腦，乜水都抽<br />\n黃毓民永遠是他們的紅太陽<br />\n盤菜瑩子俾熱狗搞完倒頭來繼續搞個人崇拜，亳無吸取教訓<br />\n抽錯水抹黑人，事其事是非其非，幾時屌下自己？<br />\n<br />\n證據：<br />\n<br />\n東方昇全版廣告單野，杜汶澤係咪柒左？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1090422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1090422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤算唔算係典型黃毓民弱智信徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1091484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1091484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n臭閪盤菜瑩子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0AeQ04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0AeQ04.png&h=7ca8d373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZnptN5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZnptN5.png&h=dcdeb69d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認住呢班賤人！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b4f915d955d6bc12dd9232474f508c8d611cac9","tid":1093603,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"好心仇思達條柒頭, 幾十歲人仲拿本由未畢業大學生係2014年寫既《香港民族論》洋洋萬字之中挑一句黎大造文章, 嘈到2019年<br />\n<br />\n大蝦細呀？仇思達知唔知個「醜」字點寫？<br />\n<br />\n有種你仇思達就拿《香港民族源流史》、《中國窪地》、《香港獨立論》呢D出黎挑機呀？<br />\n<br />\n唔係一句話「我唔需要識, 唔需要知」就過到關架喎<br />\n<br />\n你夠膽咩？正廢物"},{"pid":"9bb0d3ec8291679337d35069a87b1e152523644b","tid":1093603,"uid":245856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T19:01:48.000Z","msg":"會唔會太誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909b6fb22514edb7de36f2e95cd6d312d90498d7","tid":1093603,"uid":216817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6eda1c9bb1e497f3eb063629631d15987f9062b2","tid":1093603,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274686b87567afbd811f81a4bc612eb85647ab9f","tid":1093603,"uid":187729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T10:00:50.000Z","msg":"成班菠蘿雞"},{"pid":"28b8ae34c558515761c3dd733495cb3ff2238d97","tid":1093603,"uid":69528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T10:13:34.000Z","msg":"鍾意得姜濤個人邊會有智慧"},{"pid":"1b2915a88eea74205f8cef2a066440fe3e84d9a8","tid":1093603,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}